<div type="abstract"><head>Peter III. Haller und Peter I. Volckamer an Heinrich Nothafft zu Wernberg, Viztum in Niederbayern</head><p>Die Absender teilen die Bereitschaft des Rates zu Nürnberg zu einer Anhörung  mit Friedrich von Egloffstein vor dem Adressaten bis Obersten Tag mit, wenn acht Tage davor und danach die Sicherheit der Beteiligten garantiert wird, und bitten um Ansetzung an einem günstig gelegenen Ort und rechtzeitige Ankündigung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_248" id="124r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_248_r2l10"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft ʒu <expan>vvermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l11">vıcʒtum Jn Nıder Payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_248_r2l12"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum als Jr vns <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . von <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Eglof - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l13">ſtein <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vvıe eẅch der <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hab . daʒ er <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für eẅch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l14">den <expan>Truchſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt Jm <expan>brıng<ex>en</ex></expan> well etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l15"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıben</expan> daʒ vns geraten deẅcht ob es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l16">eẅch gefellıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> daʒ Jr <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt . be </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l17"><expan>ſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> hett für ewch ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo hofften wır ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnd vom Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l18"><expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> Jr <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch für eẅch darcʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / Alſ da ʒu <expan>berede<ex>n</ex></expan> vvıe es von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l19">einr kerung vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> artıkel <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> beſteen ſölt . auf das ob dıe ſach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l20">hinnach ʒu <expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan> tegen <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſölt daʒ es denn deſt neher vns <expan>rıchtıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l21">Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>yecʒıg<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> vom Rat fürbracht vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l22"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> laſſen . Dıe <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ernſt vnd treẅ in den <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l23">ſıe meinen <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> geſchrıft als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l24">alſo nach ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd dıe Jren für eẅch ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vvenn Jr Jn vnd dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l25"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> Oberſt ſchıerıſt alſo für eẅch ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l26">kündet . Alſo wer auf beıd <expan>ſeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> darcʒu <expan>reıte<ex>n</ex></expan> wurd . daʒ <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> acht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l27">tag dauor vnd acht tag darnach <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> . ſıcher ſein <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l28">wır eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ . daʒ Jr ſölıch <expan>fürkom<ex>en</ex></expan> . für eẅch <expan>gelegenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l29">ſecʒen vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒeıtlıch gnug vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet vvan es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l30"><expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> alſo gewant ıſt . daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnd Jr <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . ſwerlıch alſuerr <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l31"><expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> als Jr ſelb wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mugt / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l32"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> mıt <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Volkm<ex>eir</ex>s</expan> Jnſıgel / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> andree </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l33"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> haller <expan>ſe<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">or</hi></expan> Vnd Peter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l34">volkmeır ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_248" id="124r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft zu
                        <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, vicztum in Niderpayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        vom Eglofstein <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> wie ewch der
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hab, daz er
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für ewch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        den <expan>Truchsess<ex>en</ex></expan> mit im
                            <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan> well etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schriben</expan>,
                        daz uns geraten dewcht, ob es ewch gefellich <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e,</expan>
                        daz ir <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> vom
                            <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt be<expan>schaid<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        hett, für ewch zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so hofften wir,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd vom rate
                            <expan>sölte<ex>n</ex></expan> ir <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
                        auch für ewch darczu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, als da zu
                                <expan>berede<ex>n,</ex></expan> wie es von einr kerung und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> artikel <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        besteen sölt, auf das, ob die sach hinnach zu
                            <expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan> tegen <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sölt, daz es denn dest neher uns <expan>richtig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>. Also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>yeczig<ex>en</ex></expan> brief <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> vom rat fürbracht und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> lassen, die
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ernst und trew in den
                            <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol und sie meinen
                                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> geschrift, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        noch also nach zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und die iren für ewch zu
                                <expan>schik<ex>en,</ex></expan> wenn ir in und dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">oberst schierist</q>06.01.1415</note>
</app> also für ewch verkündet, also wer auf beid
                            <expan>seite<ex>n</ex></expan> darczu <expan>reite<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wurd, daz <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> acht tag davor und acht tag
                        darnach <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> sicher sein
                                <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir sölich
                                <expan>fürkom<ex>en</ex></expan> für ewch
                                <expan>gelegenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> seczen und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> zeitlich gnug vor
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, wan es
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> also gewant ist, daz
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd ir
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> swerlich alsverr
                                <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>muge<ex>n,</ex></expan> als ir selb wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mugt; denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>V<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan> mit
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Volkm<ex>eir</ex>s</expan> insigel. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Andree. <lb/><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        Haller <expan>se<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">or</hi></expan> und Peter Volkmeir
                        zu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
